This map was created by Me and Bob Loblaw. 

It consists of:

Two unique cells that are different from any others seen on a Hosties map.

It has a large curved wall in front of the terrorist spawn and another smaller wall facing the two cells, this is extremely helpful for ct's when giving commands. 

It has a gun toss ramp.

A s4s

and a long rebel way to make t's feel happy.

You'll have to check it out for yourself
